# PI Report — Todo #47: Implement uiSlice (zustand)

## Summary
Implemented `src/store/slices/ui.ts` with the pure UI state that is safe to centralize now from App.tsx:

- **`loading: boolean`** — global loading indicator (used by sign-in form and email list drawer)
- **`error: string | null`** — top-level error string (set by any IMAP failure, cleared on sign-out or new fetch)
- **Actions:** `setLoading`, `setError`, `clearError`, `resetUi`

Design decisions:
- `bodyLoading` excluded — belongs in `EmailsSlice` (scoped to body drawer, per emails slice doc)
- `activeSender` / drawer-open state excluded — derived from `SendersSlice.activeSender` and `EmailsSlice.body`
- `searchQuery` / `unreadOnly` excluded — belongs in `SendersSlice` (bubble-view filters)
- `resetUi()` clears both `loading` and `error` for sign-out / account-swap flows
- No IMAP data fetching in this slice (pure UI state only)

